                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="modal-footer">
                                                            <button class="btn btn-primary" data-modal-close>I Understand</button>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <!-- Privacy Policy Modal -->
                                                <div class="modal-overlay" id="privacy-modal">
                                                    <div class="modal modal-lg">
                                                        <div class="modal-header">
                                                            <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
                                                            <button class="modal-close" data-modal-close>
                                                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                                                    <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                                                                    <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                                                                </svg>
                                                            </button>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="modal-body legal-content">
                                                            <p class="legal-updated">Last Updated: February 10, 2026</p>
                                                            <p class="legal-compliance">This policy complies with the <strong>Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA
                                                                10173)</strong> of the Philippines and the <strong>General Data Protection Regulation
                                                                (GDPR)</strong> of the European Union.</p>

                                                                <h4>1. Data Controller</h4>
                                                                <p>Your organization acts as the Data Controller. ThinkBridge Technologies acts as the Data Processor,
                                                                    processing personal data on behalf of your organization.</p>

                                                                    <h4>2. Personal Data We Collect</h4>
                                                                    <ul>
                                                                        <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Name, employee ID, job title, department</li>
                                                                        <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Email address, phone number</li>
                                                                        <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, login timestamps, device information</li>
                                                                        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> System activity logs, feature usage, session duration</li>
                                                                    </ul>

                                                                    <h4>3. Legal Basis for Processing</h4>
                                                                    <p>Under RA 10173 and GDPR, we process your data based on:</p>
                                                                    <ul>
                                                                        <li><strong>Consent:</strong> Your explicit agreement to these terms</li>
                                                                        <li><strong>Contractual Necessity:</strong> To provide ERP services to your organization</li>
                                                                        <li><strong>Legitimate Interests:</strong> System security, fraud prevention, service improvement</li>
                                                                        <li><strong>Legal Obligation:</strong> Compliance with applicable laws and regulations</li>
                                                                    </ul>

                                                                    <h4>4. How We Use Your Data</h4>
                                                                    <ul>
                                                                        <li>Authenticate and authorize system access</li>
                                                                        <li>Provide and maintain ERP functionality</li>
                                                                        <li>Generate audit logs for security and compliance</li>
                                                                        <li>Send system notifications and updates</li>
                                                                        <li>Improve system performance and user experience</li>
                                                                    </ul>

                                                                    <h4>5. Data Retention</h4>
                                                                    <p>Personal data is retained for the duration of your employment with the subscribing organization, plus 5
                                                                        years for audit and legal compliance purposes, unless a longer retention period is required by law.</p>

                                                                        <h4>6. Your Data Subject Rights</h4>
                                                                        <p>Under RA 10173 and GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
                                                                        <ul>
                                                                            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
                                                                            <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
                                                                            <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data (subject to legal retention requirements)
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
                                                                            <li><strong>Object:</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
                                                                            <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Withdraw consent at any time (contact your Company Administrator)
                                                                            </li>
                                                                        </ul>

                                                                        <h4>7. Data Security</h4>
                                                                        <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures including:</p>
                                                                        <ul>
                                                                            <li>End-to-end encryption for data in transit (TLS 1.3)</li>
                                                                            <li>AES-256 encryption for data at rest</li>
                                                                            <li>Role-based access control (RBAC)</li>
                                                                            <li>Regular security audits and penetration testing</li>
                                                                            <li>Multi-factor authentication options</li>
                                                                        </ul>

                                                                        <h4>8. Data Transfers</h4>
                                                                        <p>Data may be processed in servers located within the Philippines and other jurisdictions with adequate
                                                                            data protection. Cross-border transfers comply with NPC Circular 2016-02 and GDPR Chapter V
                                                                            requirements.</p>

                                                                            <h4>9. Third-Party Disclosure</h4>
                                                                            <p>We do not sell personal data. Data may be shared with:</p>
                                                                            <ul>
                                                                                <li>Cloud infrastructure providers (under Data Processing Agreements)</li>
                                                                                <li>Law enforcement when required by valid legal process</li>
                                                                                <li>Auditors for compliance verification</li>
                                                                            </ul>

                                                                            <h4>10. Breach Notification</h4>
                                                                            <p>In the event of a personal data breach, we will notify the National Privacy Commission (NPC) and affected
                                                                                data subjects within 72 hours, as required by RA 10173 and GDPR.</p>

                                                                                <h4>11. Data Protection Officer</h4>
                                                                                <p>For privacy concerns or to exercise your rights, contact:<br>
                                                                                    <strong>Data Protection Officer</strong><br>
                                                                                    Email: dpo@thinkbridge.com<br>
                                                                                    You may also file a complaint with the National Privacy Commission (NPC) at complaints@privacy.gov.ph
                                                                                </p>

                                                                                <h4>12. Policy Updates</h4>
                                                                                <p>This policy may be updated periodically. Material changes will be communicated via system notification or
                                                                                    email.</p>
                                                                                </div>
                                                                                <div class="modal-footer">
                                                                                    <button class="btn btn-primary" data-modal-close>I Understand</button>
                                                                                </div>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>

                                                                        <script>
                                                                            const turnstileSiteKey = '@turnstileSiteKey';
                                                                            let loginTurnstileWidgetId = null;
                                                                            let forgotTurnstileWidgetId = null;

                                                                            window.onTurnstileLoad = function () {
                                                                                if (!turnstileSiteKey || !window.turnstile) {
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                const loginContainer = document.getElementById('login-turnstile');
                                                                                if (loginContainer && loginTurnstileWidgetId === null) {
                                                                                    loginTurnstileWidgetId = window.turnstile.render(loginContainer, {
                                                                                        sitekey: turnstileSiteKey,
                                                                                        theme: 'light'
                                                                                    });
                                                                                }

                                                                                const forgotContainer = document.getElementById('forgot-turnstile');
                                                                                if (forgotContainer && forgotTurnstileWidgetId === null) {
                                                                                    forgotTurnstileWidgetId = window.turnstile.render(forgotContainer, {
                                                                                        sitekey: turnstileSiteKey,
                                                                                        theme: 'light'
                                                                                    });
                                                                                }
                                                                            };

                                                                            function getTurnstileToken(containerId) {
                                                                                const container = document.getElementById(containerId);
                                                                                const tokenInput = container?.querySelector('input[name="cf-turnstile-response"]');
                                                                                return tokenInput?.value?.trim() || '';
                                                                            }

                                                                            function resetTurnstile(widgetId) {
                                                                                if (window.turnstile && widgetId !== null) {
                                                                                    window.turnstile.reset(widgetId);
                                                                                }
                                                                            }
                                                                        </script>
                                                                        <script src="https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js?onload=onTurnstileLoad&render=explicit" async
                                                                                defer></script>

                                                                        <script>
                                                                            // Password toggle
                                                                            document.getElementById('toggle-password').addEventListener('click', function () {
                                                                                const passwordInput = document.getElementById('password');
                                                                                const type = passwordInput.getAttribute('type') === 'password' ? 'text' : 'password';
                                                                                passwordInput.setAttribute('type', type);
                                                                            });

                                                                            // Terms and Privacy modals
                                                                            document.getElementById('terms-link').addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                                                                e.preventDefault();
                                                                                document.getElementById('terms-modal').classList.add('active');
                                                                            });

                                                                            document.getElementById('privacy-link').addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                                                                e.preventDefault();
                                                                                document.getElementById('privacy-modal').classList.add('active');
                                                                            });

                                                                            // Close modals
                                                                            document.querySelectorAll('[data-modal-close]').forEach(btn => {
                                                                                btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
                                                                                    this.closest('.modal-overlay').classList.remove('active');
                                                                                });
                                                                            });

                                                                            document.querySelectorAll('.modal-overlay').forEach(overlay => {
                                                                                overlay.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                                                                    if (e.target === this) {
                                                                                        this.classList.remove('active');
                                                                                    }
                                                                                });
                                                                            });

                                                                            const loginForm = document.getElementById('loginForm');
                                                                            const errorMessage = document.getElementById('errorMessage');
                                                                            const loginBtn = document.getElementById('loginBtn');
                                                                            const renewSubscriptionCta = document.getElementById('renewSubscriptionCta');
                                                                            const renewSubscriptionBtn = document.getElementById('renewSubscriptionBtn');
                                                                            const forgotPasswordLink = document.getElementById('forgot-password-link');
                                                                            const mfaStep = document.getElementById('mfaStep');
                                                                            const mfaMessage = document.getElementById('mfaMessage');
                                                                            const mfaEnrollment = document.getElementById('mfaEnrollment');
                                                                            const mfaQrImage = document.getElementById('mfaQrImage');
                                                                            const mfaSecretInput = document.getElementById('mfaSecret');
                                                                            const mfaManualKeyWrap = document.getElementById('mfaManualKeyWrap');
                                                                            const mfaManualKeyToggle = document.getElementById('mfaManualKeyToggle');
                                                                            const mfaTotpGroup = document.getElementById('mfaTotpGroup');
                                                                            const mfaBackupGroup = document.getElementById('mfaBackupGroup');
                                                                            const mfaCodeInput = document.getElementById('mfaCode');
                                                                            const mfaBackupCodeInput = document.getElementById('mfaBackupCode');
                                                                            const mfaToggleModeBtn = document.getElementById('mfaToggleModeBtn');
                                                                            const mfaBackToLoginBtn = document.getElementById('mfaBackToLoginBtn');
                                                                            const emailGroup = document.getElementById('email').closest('.form-group');
                                                                            const passwordGroup = document.getElementById('password').closest('.form-group');
                                                                            const captchaGroup = document.getElementById('login-turnstile').closest('.form-group');

                                                                            const loginButtonDefaultHtml = 'Sign In <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>';
                                                                            let renewalToken = '';
                                                                            let pendingMfaToken = '';
                                                                            let mfaMode = 'totp';
                                                                            let mfaEnrollmentMode = false;

                                                                            const formatLockoutTime = (totalSeconds) => {
                                                                                const minutes = Math.floor(totalSeconds / 60);
                                                                                const seconds = totalSeconds % 60;
                                                                                return `${String(minutes).padStart(2, '0')}:${String(seconds).padStart(2, '0')}`;
                                                                            };

                                                                            const hideRenewSubscriptionCta = () => {
                                                                                renewalToken = '';
                                                                                renewSubscriptionCta.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                renewSubscriptionBtn.disabled = false;
                                                                                renewSubscriptionBtn.textContent = 'Renew Subscription';
                                                                            };

                                                                            const showRenewSubscriptionCta = (token) => {
                                                                                renewalToken = token;
                                                                                renewSubscriptionCta.style.display = 'flex';
                                                                                renewSubscriptionBtn.disabled = false;
                                                                                renewSubscriptionBtn.textContent = 'Renew Subscription';
                                                                            };

                                                                            const getPrimaryButtonIdleLabel = () => {
                                                                                if (!pendingMfaToken) {
                                                                                    return loginButtonDefaultHtml;
                                                                                }

                                                                                return mfaEnrollmentMode ? 'Complete Setup' : 'Verify Code';
                                                                            };

                                                                            const setPrimaryButtonState = (loading, label) => {
                                                                                loginBtn.disabled = loading;
                                                                                loginBtn.innerHTML = loading
                                                                                    ? `<span class="spinner"></span> ${label}`
                                                                                    : getPrimaryButtonIdleLabel();
                                                                            };

                                                                            const showError = (message) => {
                                                                                errorMessage.querySelector('.error-text').textContent = message;
                                                                                errorMessage.style.display = 'block';
                                                                            };

                                                                            const hideError = () => {
                                                                                errorMessage.style.display = 'none';
                                                                            };

                                                                            const setCredentialFieldsVisible = (visible) => {
                                                                                emailGroup.style.display = visible ? '' : 'none';
                                                                                passwordGroup.style.display = visible ? '' : 'none';
                                                                                captchaGroup.style.display = visible ? '' : 'none';
                                                                                forgotPasswordLink.style.display = visible ? '' : 'none';
                                                                            };

                                                                            const setMfaMode = (mode) => {
                                                                                if (mfaEnrollmentMode) {
                                                                                    mfaMode = 'totp';
                                                                                    mfaTotpGroup.style.display = '';
                                                                                    mfaBackupGroup.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                    mfaToggleModeBtn.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                    mfaBackToLoginBtn.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                    mfaCodeInput.focus();
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                mfaMode = mode === 'backup' ? 'backup' : 'totp';
                                                                                const useBackup = mfaMode === 'backup';
                                                                                mfaTotpGroup.style.display = useBackup ? 'none' : '';
                                                                                mfaBackupGroup.style.display = useBackup ? '' : 'none';
                                                                                mfaToggleModeBtn.style.display = '';
                                                                                mfaBackToLoginBtn.style.display = '';
                                                                                mfaToggleModeBtn.textContent = useBackup
                                                                                    ? 'Use authenticator code instead'
                                                                                    : 'Use backup code instead';

                                                                                if (useBackup) {
                                                                                    mfaBackupCodeInput.focus();
                                                                                } else {
                                                                                    mfaCodeInput.focus();
                                                                                }
                                                                            };

                                                                            const resetMfaStep = () => {
                                                                                pendingMfaToken = '';
                                                                                mfaEnrollmentMode = false;
                                                                                mfaCodeInput.value = '';
                                                                                mfaBackupCodeInput.value = '';
                                                                                mfaSecretInput.value = '';
                                                                                mfaManualKeyWrap.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                mfaManualKeyToggle.textContent = "Can't scan QR? Enter key manually";
                                                                                mfaQrImage.removeAttribute('src');
                                                                                mfaEnrollment.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                mfaStep.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                setCredentialFieldsVisible(true);
                                                                                setMfaMode('totp');
                                                                            };

                                                                            const showMfaStep = (mfaToken, message, setup, isEnrollment) => {
                                                                                pendingMfaToken = mfaToken;
                                                                                mfaEnrollmentMode = !!isEnrollment;
                                                                                mfaMessage.textContent = mfaEnrollmentMode
                                                                                    ? (message || 'Set up your authenticator app to continue.')
                                                                                    : (message || 'Enter the code from your authenticator app.');
                                                                                mfaCodeInput.value = '';
                                                                                mfaBackupCodeInput.value = '';

                                                                                if (mfaEnrollmentMode && setup) {
                                                                                    mfaSecretInput.value = setup.secret || '';
                                                                                    mfaManualKeyWrap.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                    mfaManualKeyToggle.textContent = "Can't scan QR? Enter key manually";
                                                                                    const provisioningUri = setup.provisioningUri || '';
                                                                                    mfaQrImage.src = `https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=220x220&data=${encodeURIComponent(provisioningUri)}`;
                                                                                    mfaEnrollment.style.display = '';
                                                                                } else {
                                                                                    mfaSecretInput.value = '';
                                                                                    mfaManualKeyWrap.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                    mfaManualKeyToggle.textContent = "Can't scan QR? Enter key manually";
                                                                                    mfaQrImage.removeAttribute('src');
                                                                                    mfaEnrollment.style.display = 'none';
                                                                                }

                                                                                hideRenewSubscriptionCta();
                                                                                setCredentialFieldsVisible(false);
                                                                                mfaStep.style.display = 'block';
                                                                                setMfaMode('totp');
                                                                                setPrimaryButtonState(false, '');
                                                                            };

                                                                            const startLockoutTimer = (seconds, message) => {
                                                                                if (window._lockoutTimer) {
                                                                                    clearInterval(window._lockoutTimer);
                                                                                    window._lockoutTimer = null;
                                                                                }

                                                                                let remainingSeconds = seconds;
                                                                                showError(message.replace('{time}', formatLockoutTime(remainingSeconds)));
                                                                                loginBtn.disabled = true;
                                                                                loginBtn.innerHTML = `Locked (${formatLockoutTime(remainingSeconds)})`;

                                                                                window._lockoutTimer = setInterval(() => {
                                                                                    remainingSeconds--;
                                                                                    if (remainingSeconds <= 0) {
                                                                                        clearInterval(window._lockoutTimer);
                                                                                        window._lockoutTimer = null;
                                                                                        hideError();
                                                                                        loginBtn.disabled = false;
                                                                                        loginBtn.innerHTML = getPrimaryButtonIdleLabel();
                                                                                    } else {
                                                                                        showError(message.replace('{time}', formatLockoutTime(remainingSeconds)));
                                                                                        loginBtn.innerHTML = `Locked (${formatLockoutTime(remainingSeconds)})`;
                                                                                    }
                                                                                }, 1000);
                                                                            };

                                                                            renewSubscriptionBtn.onclick = async function () {
                                                                                if (!renewalToken) {
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                renewSubscriptionBtn.disabled = true;
                                                                                renewSubscriptionBtn.textContent = 'Redirecting...';

                                                                                try {
                                                                                    const renewalResponse = await fetch('/Auth/CreateRenewalCheckout', {
                                                                                        method: 'POST',
                                                                                        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                                                                                        credentials: 'same-origin',
                                                                                        body: JSON.stringify({ renewalToken: renewalToken })
                                                                                    });

                                                                                    if (!renewalResponse.ok) {
                                                                                        throw new Error(`HTTP error! status: ${renewalResponse.status}`);
                                                                                    }

                                                                                    const renewalResult = await renewalResponse.json();
                                                                                    if (renewalResult.success && renewalResult.checkoutUrl) {
                                                                                        window.location.href = renewalResult.checkoutUrl;
                                                                                        return;
                                                                                    }

                                                                                    showError(renewalResult.message || 'Unable to start renewal checkout. Please try again.');
                                                                                    renewSubscriptionBtn.disabled = false;
                                                                                    renewSubscriptionBtn.textContent = 'Renew Subscription';
                                                                                } catch (error) {
                                                                                    showError('Unable to start renewal checkout. Please try again.');
                                                                                    renewSubscriptionBtn.disabled = false;
                                                                                    renewSubscriptionBtn.textContent = 'Renew Subscription';
                                                                                }
                                                                            };

                                                                            mfaToggleModeBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
                                                                                setMfaMode(mfaMode === 'totp' ? 'backup' : 'totp');
                                                                            });

                                                                            mfaManualKeyToggle.addEventListener('click', function () {
                                                                                if (!mfaEnrollmentMode) {
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                const showManualKey = mfaManualKeyWrap.style.display === 'none';
                                                                                mfaManualKeyWrap.style.display = showManualKey ? '' : 'none';
                                                                                mfaManualKeyToggle.textContent = showManualKey
                                                                                    ? 'Hide manual key'
                                                                                    : "Can't scan QR? Enter key manually";
                                                                            });

                                                                            mfaBackToLoginBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
                                                                                resetMfaStep();
                                                                                setPrimaryButtonState(false, '');
                                                                            });

                                                                            loginForm.addEventListener('submit', async function (e) {
                                                                                e.preventDefault();

                                                                                if (window._lockoutTimer) {
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                hideError();

                                                                                if (pendingMfaToken) {
                                                                                    const verificationCode = ((mfaEnrollmentMode || mfaMode !== 'backup')
                                                                                        ? mfaCodeInput.value
                                                                                        : mfaBackupCodeInput.value).trim();
                                                                                    if (!verificationCode) {
                                                                                        showError((!mfaEnrollmentMode && mfaMode === 'backup')
                                                                                            ? 'Please enter a backup code.'
                                                                                            : 'Please enter the authenticator code.');
                                                                                        return;
                                                                                    }

                                                                                    setPrimaryButtonState(true, mfaEnrollmentMode ? 'Completing setup...' : 'Verifying...');

                                                                                    try {
                                                                                        const mfaResponse = await fetch(mfaEnrollmentMode ? '/Auth/EnrollTotp' : '/Auth/VerifyTotp', {
                                                                                            method: 'POST',
                                                                                            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                                                                                            credentials: 'same-origin',
                                                                                            body: JSON.stringify({
                                                                                                mfaToken: pendingMfaToken,
                                                                                                code: verificationCode
                                                                                            })
                                                                                        });

                                                                                        if (!mfaResponse.ok) {
                                                                                            throw new Error(`HTTP error! status: ${mfaResponse.status}`);
                                                                                        }

                                                                                        const mfaResult = await mfaResponse.json();
                                                                                        if (mfaResult.success) {
                                                                                            sessionStorage.setItem('userRole', mfaResult.user.role.toLowerCase());
                                                                                            sessionStorage.setItem('userName', mfaResult.user.name);
                                                                                            sessionStorage.setItem('userEmail', mfaResult.user.email);
                                                                                            if (Array.isArray(mfaResult.backupCodes) && mfaResult.backupCodes.length > 0) {
                                                                                                sessionStorage.setItem('tb_new_backup_codes', JSON.stringify(mfaResult.backupCodes));
                                                                                            }
                                                                                            localStorage.removeItem('tb_onboarding_done');
                                                                                            window.location.href = mfaResult.redirectUrl;
                                                                                            return;
                                                                                        }

                                                                                        if (mfaResult.lockoutSeconds > 0) {
                                                                                            startLockoutTimer(
                                                                                                mfaResult.lockoutSeconds,
                                                                                                'Too many invalid verification attempts. Please try again after {time}.'
                                                                                            );
                                                                                        } else {
                                                                                            showError(mfaResult.message || 'Verification failed. Please try again.');
                                                                                            setPrimaryButtonState(false, '');
                                                                                        }
                                                                                    } catch (error) {
                                                                                        console.error('MFA verification error:', error);
                                                                                        showError('An error occurred while verifying your code. Please try again.');
                                                                                        setPrimaryButtonState(false, '');
                                                                                    }

                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                hideRenewSubscriptionCta();

                                                                                const email = document.getElementById('email').value.toLowerCase().trim();
                                                                                const password = document.getElementById('password').value;

                                                                                if (!email) {
                                                                                    showError('Please enter your email address.');
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                if (!password) {
                                                                                    showError('Please enter your password.');
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                const captchaToken = getTurnstileToken('login-turnstile');
                                                                                if (!captchaToken) {
                                                                                    showError('Please complete the security verification.');
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                setPrimaryButtonState(true, 'Signing in...');

                                                                                try {
                                                                                    const response = await fetch('/Auth/Login', {
                                                                                        method: 'POST',
                                                                                        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                                                                                        credentials: 'same-origin',
                                                                                        body: JSON.stringify({
                                                                                            email: email,
                                                                                            password: password,
                                                                                            rememberMe: false,
                                                                                            captchaToken: captchaToken
                                                                                        })
                                                                                    });

                                                                                    if (!response.ok) {
                                                                                        throw new Error(`HTTP error! status: ${response.status}`);
                                                                                    }

                                                                                    const result = await response.json();

                                                                                    if (result.success) {
                                                                                        sessionStorage.setItem('userRole', result.user.role.toLowerCase());
                                                                                        sessionStorage.setItem('userName', result.user.name);
                                                                                        sessionStorage.setItem('userEmail', result.user.email);
                                                                                        localStorage.removeItem('tb_onboarding_done');
                                                                                        window.location.href = result.redirectUrl;
                                                                                        return;
                                                                                    }

                                                                                    resetTurnstile(loginTurnstileWidgetId);

                                                                                    if (result.requiresTotp && result.mfaToken) {
                                                                                        showMfaStep(
                                                                                            result.mfaToken,
                                                                                            result.message,
                                                                                            result.setup || null,
                                                                                            result.requiresTotpEnrollment === true
                                                                                        );
                                                                                        setPrimaryButtonState(false, '');
                                                                                        return;
                                                                                    }

                                                                                    if (result.lockoutSeconds > 0) {
                                                                                        startLockoutTimer(
                                                                                            result.lockoutSeconds,
                                                                                            'Too many failed login attempts. Please try again after {time}.'
                                                                                        );
                                                                                    } else {
                                                                                        showError(result.message || 'Login failed. Please try again.');

                                                                                        if (result.errorCode === 'subscription_expired' && result.canRenewSubscription && result.renewalToken) {
                                                                                            showRenewSubscriptionCta(result.renewalToken);
                                                                                        } else {
                                                                                            hideRenewSubscriptionCta();
                                                                                        }

                                                                                        setPrimaryButtonState(false, '');
                                                                                    }
                                                                                } catch (error) {
                                                                                    resetTurnstile(loginTurnstileWidgetId);
                                                                                    console.error('Login error:', error);
                                                                                    showError('An error occurred. Please try again.');
                                                                                    setPrimaryButtonState(false, '');
                                                                                }
                                                                            });

                                                                            // Forgot Password
                                                                            document.getElementById('forgot-password-link').addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                                                                e.preventDefault();
                                                                                // Reset modal state
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-email').value = '';
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-error').style.display = 'none';
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-password-form-container').style.display = 'block';
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-success-container').style.display = 'none';
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-footer').style.display = '';
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-done-footer').style.display = 'none';
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-submit-btn').disabled = false;
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-submit-btn').textContent = 'Send Reset Email';
                                                                                resetTurnstile(forgotTurnstileWidgetId);
                                                                                document.getElementById('forgot-password-modal').classList.add('active');
                                                                            });

                                                                            document.getElementById('forgot-submit-btn').addEventListener('click', async function () {
                                                                                const email = document.getElementById('forgot-email').value.trim().toLowerCase();
                                                                                const errorDiv = document.getElementById('forgot-error');
                                                                                const errorText = document.getElementById('forgot-error-text');
                                                                                const submitBtn = document.getElementById('forgot-submit-btn');

                                                                                errorDiv.style.display = 'none';

                                                                                if (!email) {
                                                                                    errorText.textContent = 'Please enter your email address.';
                                                                                    errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                const forgotCaptchaToken = getTurnstileToken('forgot-turnstile');
                                                                                if (!forgotCaptchaToken) {
                                                                                    errorText.textContent = 'Please complete the security verification.';
                                                                                    errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
                                                                                    return;
                                                                                }

                                                                                submitBtn.disabled = true;
                                                                                submitBtn.textContent = 'Sending...';

                                                                                try {
                                                                                    const response = await fetch('/Auth/ForgotPassword', {
                                                                                        method: 'POST',
                                                                                        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                                                                                        body: JSON.stringify({ email: email, captchaToken: forgotCaptchaToken })
                                                                                    });

                                                                                    const result = await response.json();

                                                                                    if (result.success) {
                                                                                        const successText = document.getElementById('forgot-success-text');
                                                                                        if (successText && result.message) {
                                                                                            successText.textContent = result.message;
                                                                                        }
                                                                                        document.getElementById('forgot-password-form-container').style.display = 'none';
                                                                                        document.getElementById('forgot-success-container').style.display = 'block';
                                                                                        document.getElementById('forgot-footer').style.display = 'none';
                                                                                        document.getElementById('forgot-done-footer').style.display = '';
                                                                                    } else {
                                                                                        resetTurnstile(forgotTurnstileWidgetId);
                                                                                        errorText.textContent = result.message || 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
                                                                                        errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
                                                                                        submitBtn.disabled = false;
                                                                                        submitBtn.textContent = 'Send Reset Email';
                                                                                    }
                                                                                } catch (error) {
                                                                                    resetTurnstile(forgotTurnstileWidgetId);
                                                                                    errorText.textContent = 'An error occurred. Please try again.';
                                                                                    errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
                                                                                    submitBtn.disabled = false;
                                                                                    submitBtn.textContent = 'Send Reset Email';
                                                                                }
                                                                            });
                                                                        </script>